ndow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"麻彌","body":"好的，一起加油吧！\n但是，也請小心不要受傷了喔！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"gattsu01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"ev59-ep2-018","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"麻彌","body":"裝置使用的木板很容易破掉，\n根據地方的不同，釘子尖端也有可能凸出來","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"ev59-ep2-019","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"麻彌","body":"小心不要發生事故，\n並一邊將舞台復原吧！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"ev59-ep2-020","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":16}],"windowDisplayName":"彩","body":"但是……呢。\n要把大家那麼努力才做好的舞台破壞掉……\n總覺得有點寂寞呢……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":16,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":16,"voiceId":"ev59-ep2-021","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":25}],"windowDisplayName":"燐子","body":"是、這樣呢……雖然這是……一開始就、知道的事……\n但還是、有點……寂寞呢……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":25,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":25,"voiceId":"ev59-ep2-022","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"麻彌","body":"我也是，第一次做舞台時，\n也有同樣的感受呢","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"ev59-ep2-023","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"麻彌","body":"在親手做出來的舞台裡，\n感覺留有一些自己的回憶，\n要把那些都破壞掉覺得有點捨不得……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"ev59-ep2-024","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":21}],"windowDisplayName":"友希那","body":"一些回憶？　怎麼說呢？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":21,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":21,"voiceId":"ev59-ep2-025","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"麻彌","body":"雖然也不是什麼很重要的事啦……\n譬如說，那個背板……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"ev59-ep2-026","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"麻彌","body":"因為中途把油漆用完了\n請彩小姐去幫忙買，之類的","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"ev59-ep2-027","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":16}],"windowDisplayName":"彩","body":"啊啊，沒錯，有這件事","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":16,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":16,"voiceId":"ev59-ep2-028","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"麻彌","body":"還有這邊的踏箱是，高度稍微有點不符，\n硬是用瓦楞紙箱貼上去調整，之類的","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"ev59-ep2-029","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"麻彌","body":"嗯，說起來真的都是一些小事，\n觀眾也絕對不會發現\n這是只有做出這個舞台的我們才會知道的事","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"ev59-ep2-030","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":16}],"windowDisplayName":"彩","body":"我也是，現在在桌子上的茶具，\n是在那邊的小道具店買的呢，之類的\n浮現了好多回憶呢","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":16,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":16,"voiceId":"ev59-ep2-031","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":25}],"windowDisplayName":"燐子","body":"一定是……這些小小的……累積……\n創造出……這個舞台……的吧……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":25,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":25,"voiceId":"ev59-ep2-032","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"麻彌","body":"湊小姐，這種小小的回憶，你也有嗎？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"ev59-ep2-033","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":21}],"windowDisplayName":"友希那","body":"我的話呢……應該是，服裝的鈕扣的部分吧？\n只是要縫上一顆鈕扣而已，最開始的時候卻重做了好幾遍","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":21,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":21,"voiceId":"ev59-ep2-034","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":25}],"windowDisplayName":"燐子","body":"但是……友希那同學……\n最後卻，非常熟練了呢……\n後來，縫鈕扣的部分……不小心通通都請你幫忙了……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":25,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":25,"voiceId":"ev59-ep2-035","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":21}],"windowDisplayName":"友希那","body":"那是因為，燐子很有耐心地教我喔。\n多虧你，讓我稍微有點自信了","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":21,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":21,"voiceId":"ev59-ep2-036","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"麻彌","body":"大家同心協力，一起做出一個東西！\n完成之後，一定會有什麼成長的！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"ev59-ep2-037","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":21}],"windowDisplayName":"友希那","body":"這樣的話，舞台劇也\n跟樂團活動有相通的部分也說不定呢","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":21,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":21,"voiceId":"ev59-ep2-038","volume":1}],"speed":0,"f